description: The original recording of Bud: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TaSDinL6pC8 . The big lesson I learnt was that instead of Chord scale relationships, I should be thinking of Scale-chord relationships. Scales are the most important. I once heard Barry Harris explain this in some of his youtube videos. Barry knows Bud's style inside-out.
